text: Iced coffee is not very sweet .Boss is also very friendly . Worth to give a try again !
Good teh! My iced teh was well pulled to create a nice airy frothy drink. Will come again to try their coffee
Cannot get this $0.70 coffee “O” anymore in S’pore. Ordered Kopi O Gao Siu Tai (strong coffee with little sugar), not strong enough for me, their beans are slightly sour...
Long queue because of the slow service, not because the coffee is good. Coffee tastes like left over.
Iced yuan yang was frothy and thick
